'''Shamsher Jang''' is a Hindu (Hindi?) princely title meaning ''Sword of War''.

It was part of the full style of the [[Maharaja]] of [[Travancore]]: Maharaja Raja Ramaraja Sri Patmanabha Dasa Vanchi Pala (personal name) Varma, Kulasekhara Kiritapati Manney Sultan Bahadur, Shamsher Jang, Maharaja of Travancore